	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello, do you guys know which NES/FC emulator is the most accurate in behavior to a real hardware? I am using Nestopia which looks to me as the best choice, but maybe you have other tips... Thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
